//--- PSEUDOCODE VERSION 0.1 FOR ePOS ---//

connect to database

log in by swiping a card
enter 4 digit validation pin

select popular items 
display popular items

iterate other items
	display item in grid

scan item or select on screen
	add item to array of selected items
	select quantity (default 1)
	display selected items

proceed to payment
	swipe card to simulate transaction
	
display transaction accept or decline
display receipt

adjust stock accordingly
increment number of items sold
adjust popular items list
